1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

2
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

3
00:00:11,740 --> 00:00:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

4
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 10: Hide-and-Seek Isn't Scary</font></b></font></font>

5
00:01:31,140 --> 00:01:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}There's something seriously wrong
 with that Namu guy!</i></font>

6
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ch-Chie-sensei, what's your problem
 with my master?</font>

7
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He's ridiculous!</i></font>

8
00:01:36,990 --> 00:01:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's my "problem"? 
He tried to kill Kaya-chan!</i></font>

9
00:01:40,290 --> 00:01:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a false accusation.</font>

10
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't call exorcism 
"killing" evil spirits, would you?</font>

11
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:48,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you looking after him, Mob-san?!</font>

12
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He asked to see my files on Kaya-sama.</i></font>

13
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#2d2d2c">Zero abilities</font></font></b></font></font>

14
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an7}<font size="8"><font color="#2d2d2c">\h\h\hWhere did
\h\hKaya-sama
inherit her
abilities?</font></font></b></font></font>

15
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#0a0909">Kaya-sama 
and her family</font></font></b></font></font>

16
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#0a0909">\hWhat
is "It"?</font></font></b></font></font>

17
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#0a0909">A mysterious
specter?</font></font></b></font></font>

18
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#0a0909">Derived from 
the fetus?</font></font></b></font></font>

19
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#0a0909">Huge black
shadow</font></font></b></font></font>

20
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? What on earth are you up to?</i></font>

21
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something feels off. 
A bunch of things just don't add up.</font>

22
00:01:59,890 --> 00:02:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Named after the head family's tradition. 
Eldest daughter and a psychic.</font>

23
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So she's clearly the next successor.</font>

24
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet she's out there living a normal life.</font>

25
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to top it off, 
her true form is that monster.</font>

26
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um, you said "head family." 
So you're an Ebisumori, too, then?</i></font>

27
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm from a branch of the Ebisumori clan. 
My side uses a different kanji.</font>

28
00:02:21,830 --> 00:02:24,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The head house 
holds the spiritual lineage,</font>

29
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="18"><font color="#010101">Head</font></font></b></font></font>

30
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="18"><font color="#010101">Family</font></font></b></font></font>

31
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="30"><font color="#200043">Ebisumori
<font size="14">(Warrior/Shrine grove)</font></font></font></b></font></font>

32
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the branch family descends 
from the non-psychic line.</font>

33
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="18"><font color="#010101">Branch</font></font></b></font></font>

34
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="18"><font color="#010101">Family</font></font></b></font></font>

35
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="30"><font color="#200043">Ebisumori
<font size="14">(God of fortune/Defense)</font></font></font></b></font></font>

36
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The branch families near worshiped
the head house's shrine maiden</font>

37
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:35,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and served her faithfully.</font>

38
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or something like that. Probably.</font>

39
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why is that part so vague?</i></font>

40
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you expect?</font>

41
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was kicked out of the house 
when I was about four or five.</font>

42
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's some kind of atavism,</font>

43
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I've been able to see 
the shrine maiden's true form since birth.</font>

44
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon after I spoke up about it, 
I was put into foster care.</font>

45
00:02:54,610 --> 00:02:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw <i>something</i> they would do anything 
to hide, including ruin a child's future.</font>

46
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, something far 
more monstrous even than that</font>

47
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has slipped its leash and
 is living as a kindergartner.</font>

48
00:03:07,130 --> 00:03:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Now do you see why 
I feel I have to take it out?</font>

49
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So you're still dead set on 
getting rid of Kaya-chan?</i></font>

50
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:17,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's what needs to be done.</font>

51
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You put that thing back into 
its human vessel and kept it alive.</font>

52
00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's on you to make sure
 it stays human.</font>

53
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd make things 
a lot easier for me, too.</font>

54
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As if I wouldn't!</i></font>

55
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aunt Nana!</font>

56
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just Nana, Kaya.</font>

57
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ebisumori Nana.</i></font>

58
00:03:39,510 --> 00:03:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kaya-chan's aunt, who's head of 
the main Ebisumori clan and a psychic.</i></font>

59
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chie-sensei.</font>

60
00:03:44,940 --> 00:03:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, uh, yes?</font>

61
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya seems rather listless lately.
Any ideas why that might be?</font>

62
00:03:51,790 --> 00:03:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh, let's see...</font>

63
00:03:55,480 --> 00:04:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I say? There's a possibility 
she doesn't see Kaya-chan as human.</i></font>

64
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if she has the same motive as Namu?</i></font>

65
00:04:03,940 --> 00:04:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you find out anything...</font>

66
00:04:05,930 --> 00:04:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or rather, if you feel like talking,
 please let me know.</font>

67
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure.</font>

68
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="32"><font face="Impact">{\an8}<font color="#f1b158">Fun</font></font></font></b></font>

69
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="32"><font face="Impact">{\an8}<font color="#e540a8">Origami Lesson</font></font></font></b></font>

70
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Aunt Nana—</font>

71
00:04:17,130 --> 00:04:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just call me "Nana."</font>

72
00:04:18,820 --> 00:04:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you beat up ghosts, too?</font>

73
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. Only someone as exceptional as you
 is capable of that, Kaya.</font>

74
00:04:28,550 --> 00:04:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it didn't work the other day.</font>

75
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't beat it up.</font>

76
00:04:33,590 --> 00:04:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I won't fight ghosts anymore.</font>

77
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was about your age,</font>

78
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">specters were simply terrifying.</font>

79
00:04:43,630 --> 00:04:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I could do was hide
 behind my mother.</font>

80
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not something a small child 
like you should have to face.</font>

81
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're right to avoid conflict.</font>

82
00:04:56,070 --> 00:05:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in case there comes a time when you 
need to confront them, keep this with you.</font>

83
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a talisman.</font>

84
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll protect you from specters.</font>

85
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:09,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Butt.</font>

86
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a heart.</font>

87
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

88
00:05:12,980 --> 00:05:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana.</font>

89
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this a butt?</font>

90
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a heart!</font>

91
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kidding.</font>

92
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez!</font>

93
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aunt Nana.</font>

94
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for saying it looks like a butt.</font>

95
00:05:28,650 --> 00:05:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. I just have something 
in my eyes, that's all.</font>

96
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who wants to play hide-and-seek?</font>

97
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me!</font>

98
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rock, paper, scissors!</font>

99
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're it, Kaya-chan.</font>

100
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}One. Two.</font>

101
00:05:46,330 --> 00:05:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where should I hide?</font>

102
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Three. Four.</font>

103
00:05:49,370 --> 00:05:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Five. Six.</font>

104
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna hide in here.</font>

105
00:05:53,010 --> 00:05:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saku-chan.</font>

106
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Ma-kun?</font>

107
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know a good hiding spot.</font>

108
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do?</font>

109
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew, here? I don't like the dark.</font>

110
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you wanna win the game, don't you?</font>

111
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I can hide in here for a bit.</font>

112
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nineteen. Twenty.</font>

113
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you, Ken-ken.</font>

114
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

115
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you, Yuzu-chan.</font>

116
00:06:33,910 --> 00:06:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw.</font>

117
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you, Ma-kun and Saku-chan.</font>

118
00:06:47,030 --> 00:06:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two aren't the Ma-kun 
and Saku-chan I know.</font>

119
00:06:50,140 --> 00:06:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

120
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

121
00:06:53,810 --> 00:06:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weirdo.</font>

122
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's so weird.</font>

123
00:07:00,050 --> 00:07:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a weird kid 
that says weird things.</font>

124
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saku-chan would never say that to me!</font>

125
00:07:11,330 --> 00:07:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it.
There's nothing you can do.</font>

126
00:07:15,330 --> 00:07:19,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go away. You can't play with us.</font>

127
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you climb all the way up—</font>

128
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where's Kaya-chan?</font>

129
00:07:24,140 --> 00:07:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she doesn't wanna play anymore.</font>

130
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's keep playing 
hide-and-seek with just us.</font>

131
00:07:33,530 --> 00:07:35,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ken-ken!</font>

132
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I give up! You can come out now.</font>

133
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did he go?</font>

134
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who cares? We're gonna be late 
for pickup. Just leave him.</font>

135
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! We were playing together, 
so you have to help me find him.</font>

136
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ken-ken!</font>

137
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to go home!</font>

138
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come out already!</font>

139
00:07:58,730 --> 00:07:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

140
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you, Ken-ken!</font>

141
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hurry back to class.</font>

142
00:08:05,230 --> 00:08:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yuzu.</font>

143
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look like you're gonna cry.</font>

144
00:08:11,610 --> 00:08:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it 'cause you saw it?</font>

145
00:08:18,810 --> 00:08:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, time to go home.</font>

146
00:08:21,810 --> 00:08:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

147
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to go.</font>

148
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan!</font>

149
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all acting weird!</font>

150
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help—</font>

151
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Yuzu-chan!</font>

152
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't like monsters, do you?</font>

153
00:08:39,970 --> 00:08:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be good and nothing scary will happen.</font>

154
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it. 
There's nothing you can do.</font>

155
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in case there comes a time when you 
need to confront them, keep this with you.</font>

156
00:08:59,090 --> 00:09:05,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't find us 
'cause we found an amazing hiding spot.</font>

157
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No! Stop it!</font>

158
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let me go!</font>

159
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody will ever find you in here.</font>

160
00:09:18,290 --> 00:09:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hide together. 
We can hide here forever and ever.</font>

161
00:09:23,290 --> 00:09:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because nobody will find you.</font>

162
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forever and ever.</font>

163
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan?</font>

164
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

165
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, she got away.</font>

166
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, whatever. This one will do.</font>

167
00:09:55,050 --> 00:09:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

168
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away!</font>

169
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want you!</font>

170
00:10:03,210 --> 00:10:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you be mean...</font>

171
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to my friends!</font>

172
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't open! Somebody, help me!</font>

173
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, don't shut the door! Open up!</font>

174
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's so dark and scary!</font>

175
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

176
00:10:22,850 --> 00:10:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you.</font>

177
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

178
00:10:25,180 --> 00:10:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

179
00:10:27,420 --> 00:10:30,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you all doing over there?!</font>

180
00:10:31,650 --> 00:10:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

181
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan! You guys!</font>

182
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good! You're all back to normal!</font>

183
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's going on here?</font>

184
00:10:44,830 --> 00:10:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. Let's go back to our classroom.</font>

185
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan.</font>

186
00:10:49,890 --> 00:10:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beat up the ghost.</font>

187
00:10:52,070 --> 00:10:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not sure why, 
but she seems like herself again.</i></font>

188
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:58,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did? Thank you.</font>

189
00:10:58,150 --> 00:11:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look. Aunt Nana gave me this.</font>

190
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From Nana-san, huh?</font>

191
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a talisman.</font>

192
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. That's a surprise.</font>

193
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan, can I see what's inside?</font>

194
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

195
00:11:18,260 --> 00:11:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

196
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Cameras Aren't Scary</font></b></font></font>

197
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're really good, Kaya-chan.</font>

198
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard she wasn't herself lately,</font>

199
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm glad she's okay.</font>

200
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:42,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this your usual thing, Osamu-kun?</font>

201
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for making you come along, Master.</font>

202
00:11:45,890 --> 00:11:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. We're dealing with the head family.</font>

203
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows what could happen 
if I leave you alone again?</font>

204
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:52,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's use this next.</font>

205
00:11:52,940 --> 00:11:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You listening?</font>

206
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Snap.</font>

207
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you don't know this, but when it 
comes to recording spiritual phenomena,</font>

208
00:11:59,990 --> 00:12:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">analog is the way to go.</font>

209
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see anything.</font>

210
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It takes time to develop the image.</font>

211
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah. Now I see—</font>

212
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Analog methods can sometimes reveal 
truths the human eye can't detect.</font>

213
00:12:17,420 --> 00:12:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thirsty, so I'm gonna 
buy us some drinks.</font>

214
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#b2b7d8">Cold</font></font></b></font>

215
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#b2b7d8">Cold</font></font></b></font>

216
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="9"><font color="#b2b7d8">Cold</font></font></b></font>

217
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="9"><font color="#b2b7d8">Cold</font></font></b></font>

218
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8"><font color="#b2b7d8">Cold</font></font></b></font>

219
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="10"><font color="#31302f">Stronger
Scent!</font></font></font>

220
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="10"><font color="#31302f">Stronger
Scent!</font></font></font>

221
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="9"><font color="#504f4e">Stronger
Scent!</font></font></font>

222
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="6"><font color="#706e69">A Golden Gift</font></font></b></font></font>

223
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="10"><font color="#b45f5b">Apple</font></font></b></font></font>

224
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Truths the human eye can't detect," huh?</font>

225
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! Hop, hop.</font>

226
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not seeing any irregularities 
that Chie-sensei or Master mentioned.</font>

227
00:12:40,580 --> 00:12:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it only manifest 
under certain conditions?</font>

228
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait. That's...</font>

229
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as I thought. 
It's something not of this world.</font>

230
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Analog really makes a difference.</font>

231
00:12:56,140 --> 00:12:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since Kaya-sama left it alone,</font>

232
00:12:59,010 --> 00:13:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it likely hasn't developed into a specter
 that can harm people yet.</font>

233
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it looking at me?</font>

234
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It noticed me!</font>

235
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad, Osamu-kun. 
I dropped the photo some—</font>

236
00:13:16,810 --> 00:13:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you standing stock-still?</font>

237
00:13:18,990 --> 00:13:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Master, please take a look
 at these photos.</font>

238
00:13:26,450 --> 00:13:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It moves every time I look away.</font>

239
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet it's the kind of specter that 
attacks when you take your eyes off it.</font>

240
00:13:34,390 --> 00:13:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can see it, right, Master?</font>

241
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you please take it out?</font>

242
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really need to blink soon. 
My eyes are drying out!</font>

243
00:13:41,220 --> 00:13:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could, but I don't see 
any specter around here.</font>

244
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

245
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in reality...</font>

246
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:53,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's strange. 
Osamu-kun sees it, but I don't?</i></font>

247
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Osamu-kun.</font>

248
00:13:54,970 --> 00:13:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes?</font>

249
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look.</font>

250
00:13:56,860 --> 00:14:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, you mustn't!
The specter will attack if you don't—</font>

251
00:14:00,530 --> 00:14:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There it is.</font>

252
00:14:04,170 --> 00:14:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha.</font>

253
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was careless of me. 
I should have seen you.</font>

254
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiding inside the camera is 
pretty slick, I'll give you that.</font>

255
00:14:21,130 --> 00:14:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was close! I still have my eyes.</font>

256
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, Osamu-kun?</font>

257
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you very—</font>

258
00:14:28,610 --> 00:14:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It multiplied. But how?</font>

259
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. You're pretty clever, aren't you?</font>

260
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Master!</font>

261
00:14:40,250 --> 00:14:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help you right now. 
Get out of here while it's focused on me!</font>

262
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't!</font>

263
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

264
00:14:55,590 --> 00:14:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't bully...</font>

265
00:14:58,420 --> 00:14:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mobuo's friends.</font>

266
00:15:10,020 --> 00:15:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mobuo, are you okay?</font>

267
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-sama!</font>

268
00:15:14,730 --> 00:15:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do that again so I can take
 a picture. Wait, no. A video!</font>

269
00:15:19,050 --> 00:15:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always the one who protects 
Osamu-kun, aren't you?</font>

270
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The boy Aunt Nana.</font>

271
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Master! Where are you going?</font>

272
00:15:27,490 --> 00:15:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

273
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't think it would get this bad.</i></font>

274
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't protect Osamu-kun like this.</i></font>

275
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't like it, 
but I guess I have no choice.</i></font>

276
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Aunt Nana Isn't Scary?</font></b></font></font>

277
00:15:42,050 --> 00:15:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Um, Ebisumori-san?</font>

278
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes? What is it?</font>

279
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This may sound ridiculous, 
but Kaya-chan can see ghosts.</font>

280
00:15:51,110 --> 00:15:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only that, she can 
get rid of them, too.</font>

281
00:15:53,940 --> 00:16:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But something out of this world 
is giving her that power, right?</font>

282
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sounds like you also know 
about Ebisumori's shrine maidens.</font>

283
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:08,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tell you what I know about Kaya-chan.</font>

284
00:16:08,780 --> 00:16:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please tell me what you know about her.</font>

285
00:16:13,370 --> 00:16:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why have you decided to 
trust me all of a sudden?</font>

286
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because she showed me.</font>

287
00:16:20,430 --> 00:16:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw what was written
 inside her talisman.</font>

288
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="15"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#0a0b0a">Let every curse 
be laid upon 
Ebisumori Nana</font></b></font></font></font>

289
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My abilities are limited. That thing 
is little more than modest comfort.</font>

290
00:16:28,430 --> 00:16:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm no different. So please...</font>

291
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to make sure Kaya-chan 
can stay with her family,</font>

292
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that no one will ever 
call her a monster again.</font>

293
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial">{\an7}<font size="40"><font color="#674d42">Conference Room</font></font></font></b></font>

294
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan is Ebisumori's shrine maiden.
That's what a person named Namu told me.</font>

295
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the son of the branch family 
is doing well. That's good to hear.</font>

296
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Namu is half correct.</font>

297
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Half?</font>

298
