<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#1e1a15">Husband</font></font></font></b></font>

313
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#1e1a15">Mutsu</font></font></font></b></font>

314
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#1e1a15">Nana</font></font></font></b></font>

315
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#1e1a15">Mirai</font></font></font></b></font>

316
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#1e1a15">Ebisumori
Family Tree</font></font></font></b></font>

317
00:16:57,540 --> 00:17:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The eldest daughter of 
the Ebisumori clan becomes a psychic."</font>

318
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strictly speaking, this is incorrect.</font>

319
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They bear children in a way that ensures
 the firstborn becomes a psychic.</font>

320
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they're deliberately creating psychics?</font>

321
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to believe, but the Ebisumoris'
 ancestor was said to be divine.</font>

322
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it was her supernatural gifts 
that led the family to great prosperity.</font>

323
00:17:20,220 --> 00:17:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, her power wasn't passed down
 to the next generation.</font>

324
00:17:25,010 --> 00:17:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even so, the Ebisumori family refused 
to give up on preserving their power.</font>

325
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:32,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pursuing the shrine maiden's rebirth,
the family tried all manner of ritual,</font>

326
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and finally discovered a method.
 And that was...</font>

327
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="50"><b><font face="Georgia"><font color="#000000">Curse</font></font></b></font></font>

328
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="50"><b><font face="Georgia"><font color="#000000">Gestation</font></font></b></font></font>

329
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Curse Gestation.</font>

330
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Children born by this method 
were always female,</font>

331
00:17:43,630 --> 00:17:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and as they matured, 
their looks and abilities</font>

332
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">mirrored the founding shrine maiden,</font>

333
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">allowing the Ebisumori family
 to flourish further.</font>

334
00:17:52,030 --> 00:17:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The shrine maidens naturally desired
 to beget the next generation,</font>

335
00:17:56,350 --> 00:18:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a lineage where the eldest daughter
inherited psychic powers was born.</font>

336
00:18:00,690 --> 00:18:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The potency of our powers varies, 
but we're all copies of her.</font>

337
00:18:03,770 --> 00:18:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="22"><font color="#1e1a15">\h\h\hIchi
<font size="12">(Ebisumori
family 
ancestor)</font></font></font></font></b></font>

338
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given that we're nothing more 
than vessels for psychic power,</font>

339
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Namu calling us "specters" 
isn't entirely wrong.</font>

340
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said Kaya-chan's inner self 
had completely turned into a specter.</font>

341
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean the girl who was 
the <i>real</i> Sato Kaya is no longer...</font>

342
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

343
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like Namu said,</font>

344
00:18:24,770 --> 00:18:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya seems to have inherited the shrine 
maiden's powers more than anyone else.</font>

345
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But who she is inside?
That's unquestionably all her.</font>

346
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

347
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm positive. Because Mirai
gave birth to Kaya and she...</font>

348
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

349
00:18:44,730 --> 00:18:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a relief. But why did Kaya-chan's
 mother go through that ritual?</font>

350
00:18:50,940 --> 00:18:53,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps it was an act of defiance.</font>

351
00:18:54,390 --> 00:18:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She felt inferior because
she didn't possess psychic powers.</font>

352
00:18:59,260 --> 00:19:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there were signs she resented 
our mother for treating us differently.</font>

353
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps after learning 
of the ritual somehow,</font>

354
00:19:07,140 --> 00:19:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she wanted to free herself
 from those feelings</font>

355
00:19:09,770 --> 00:19:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by making her daughter a psychic.</font>

356
00:19:13,210 --> 00:19:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's probably why 
she named her daughter "Kaya,"</font>

357
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">using the kanji for "God"
 and the "number eight."</font>

358
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that explains her second baby.</font>

359
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:23,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Second baby?</font>

360
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. A psychic guy I know said</font>

361
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan's mother is pregnant
 with a specter.</font>

362
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So she went through 
another Curse Gestation, right?</font>

363
00:19:34,690 --> 00:19:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She probably wants her daughters 
to be psychics because she couldn't.</font>

364
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not possible.</font>

365
00:19:40,890 --> 00:19:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no doubt Kaya was born 
as the shrine maiden.</font>

366
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Mirai ran off with my...</font>

367
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if she wanted <i>another</i> baby...</font>

368
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, Nana-san?</font>

369
00:19:54,390 --> 00:19:58,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. There's something I need
 to go check. If you'll excuse us.</font>

370
00:19:58,270 --> 00:19:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

371
00:20:01,380 --> 00:20:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, hey!</font>

372
00:20:03,010 --> 00:20:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye, Chie-sensei.</font>

373
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="25"><font color="#214125">Nurses' 
Station</font></font></b></font>

374
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here to see Sato Mirai.</font>

375
00:20:10,370 --> 00:20:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">End of the corridor, to the right.</font>

376
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know where she is, right, Kaya-chan? 
Show her the way.</font>

377
00:20:18,870 --> 00:20:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go.</font>

378
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're such a strong girl, Kaya.</font>

379
00:20:26,570 --> 00:20:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been dealing with your mom
 all by yourself.</font>

380
00:20:29,230 --> 00:20:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll handle it from here.</font>

381
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be right back.</font>

382
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To tell you the truth,
 before asking for your help with Kaya,</font>

383
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked Mirai how she felt about it,</font>

384
00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because you said things were complicated.</font>

385
00:20:48,210 --> 00:20:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Mirai said with a smile...</font>

386
00:20:50,990 --> 00:20:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show her to my sister. 
She'll be surprised.</font>

387
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mirai, what are you trying to do?</i></font>

388
00:21:01,450 --> 00:21:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="25"><font color="#a7a69f">Sato Mirai</font></font></font>

389
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="25"><font color="#a7a69f">Sato Mirai</font></font></font>

390
00:21:02,820 --> 00:21:02,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="25"><font color="#a7a69f">Sato Mirai</font></font></font>

391
00:21:02,950 --> 00:21:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="25"><font color="#a7a69f">Sato Mirai</font></font></font>

392
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="25"><font color="#a7a69f">Sato Mirai</font></font></font>

393
00:21:08,990 --> 00:21:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana-chan.</font>

394
00:21:19,430 --> 00:21:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

395
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aunt Nana!</font>

396
00:21:22,830 --> 00:21:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your nose is bleeding. Are you okay?</font>

397
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

398
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was it a hallucination? No, there was
definitely something in that room.</i></font>

399
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it attacked me.</i></font>

400
00:21:35,990 --> 00:21:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How am I still alive?</i></font>

401
00:21:40,750 --> 00:21:42,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Ebisumori speaking.</font>

402
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

403
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

404
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nana-san?</i></font>

405
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>U-Um, is everything okay?</i></font>

406
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just now?</font>

407
00:21:57,930 --> 00:22:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, I'm afraid to say your mother...</i></font>

408
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>passed away moments ago.</i></font>

409
00:22:05,430 --> 00:22:09,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<b><font size="18"><font face="Impact"><font color="#2e2725">Let every curse be laid
upon Ebisumori Mutsu</font></font></font></b></font>

